snippet.title: Video: Eva Longoria and other stars shine on L'Oreal Paris catwalk at PFW
snippet.description:
Video: Eva Longoria and other stars shine on L'Oreal Paris catwalk at PFW
Stars shine on L'Oreal Paris catwalk at Paris Fashion Week. Celebrities including British supermodel Naomi Campbell sat on the front row for the show. Actress Amber Heard and pop star Camilla Cabello made in their first-ever appearances at the show.
